data.description: Beautiful Ranch Home in Move-In condition in the lovely Marabar Heights Neighborhood!  Freshly painted and meticulously maintained with gleaming hardwood floors throughout!  Updated kitchen with butcher block counter tops and stainless steel appliances! 3 bedrooms with an attached half bathroom to the master bedroom! The full basement has been well updated for additional living space and plenty of storage! Serene backyard setting with mature trees, a large deck for entertaining and a flat yard space to enjoy!  Low traffic location, but within 2 miles of highway access and also within short distance to so many local amenities!
